{"tid":1282435,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【網絡安全】如何匿名免費咁放資料上Ethereum測試網絡","createTime":"2019-07-03T14:42:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T06:15:14.000Z","uid":159913,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2ede051321e9e24f081c6363de754b313544426e","tid":1282435,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:42:50.000Z","msg":"<strong>I) Ethereum wallet設定</strong><br />\n1. 要用Chrome/ Firefox/ Opera/ Brave瀏覽器<br />\n2. 安裝Metamask瀏覽器插件 (Chrome用家: <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/metamask/nkbihfbeogaeaoehlefnkodbefgpgknn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fmetamask%2Fnkbihfbeogaeaoehlefnkodbefgpgknn&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHl%2BAd7ywbQ%2FyO%2FBW%2BNKOVGM%3D&h=1d028f6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/metamask/nkbihfbeogaeaoehlefnkodbefgpgknn</a>)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5px5Xs2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5px5Xs2.png&h=62dc9763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3. 裝完右上角menu應該見到狐狸icon，禁入去會見到歡迎畫面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Vz8aN3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Vz8aN3.png&h=66202e61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4. Get started- Create a wallet- I agree<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cc3T6mp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCc3T6mp.png&h=69839732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5. 設定8個位嘅Metamask密碼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKxtVeK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKxtVeK.png&h=21c38d03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6. 禁個鎖(Click here to Reveal Secret Words)，會出現12組英文詞語，呢個係你Ethereum wallet嘅private key，請抄底或者backup，因為唔見咗會入唔返原本嘅Ethereum wallet (如果wallet用嚟即用即棄就唔太重要)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMtwS1q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMtwS1q.png&h=3d161d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7. 順次序禁返一次俾佢，完成setup<br />\n<br />\n<strong>II) 攞Test Ether</strong><br />\n1. 禁隻狐狸仔，上方由Main Ethereum Network轉去Ropsten Test Network (Ethereum測試網絡)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zh2mvOe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzh2mvOe.png&h=45ae3859&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. 禁Account1個位，copy你個Ropsten testnet address<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7PKv8zU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7PKv8zU.png&h=bbbb98a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3. 去攞測試用嘅Ethereum <a href=\"https://faucet.ropsten.be/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffaucet.ropsten.be%2F&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHl%2BAd7ywbQ%2FyO%2FBW%2BNKOVGM%3D&h=b35fd478\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://faucet.ropsten.be/</a> (免費)，貼返你個Ropsten testnet address上去，然後禁send me test Ether<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VRC5Xs6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVRC5Xs6.png&h=a0b35fdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4. 過一陣你account會多咗一粒testnet Ether<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ODTAAeM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FODTAAeM.png&h=bf95dce9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>III) 準備data</strong><br />\n1. 將想send嘅訊息放上 Text to Hex Converter <a href=\"https://www.online-toolz.com/tools/text-hex-convertor.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.online-toolz.com%2Ftools%2Ftext-hex-convertor.php&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHl%2BAd7ywbQ%2FyO%2FBW%2BNKOVGM%3D&h=1a2695a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.online-toolz.com/tools/text-hex-convertor.php</a> 中間唔可以分段，然後禁convert<br />\n2. 得出一串Hex output，留底備用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8PgjGy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8PgjGy.png&h=5f3318a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>IV) 放data上blockchain transaction</strong><br />\n1. 去Myetherwallet <a href=\"https://www.myetherwallet.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.myetherwallet.com%2F&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHl%2BAd7ywbQ%2FyO%2FBW%2BNKOVGM%3D&h=6cf50306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.myetherwallet.com/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM8XOzO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM8XOzO.png&h=0b98c8f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2. 禁Access my wallet- Metamask<br />\n3. Accept terms 容許Myetherwallet讀取你嘅Metamask wallet<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XdWnfeO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXdWnfeO.png&h=82cab785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4. 入咗Myetherwallet，send個transaction去自己address，打開Advanced右邊Data &amp; Gas Limit，喺Add Data貼返(III)嘅output<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FdSE1UR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFdSE1UR.png&h=1b1f949c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 5. 喺Myetherwallet禁完send transaction，再喺Metamask popup禁confirm<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hE5OVeS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhE5OVeS.png&h=8768659d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6. 等一陣就有popup彈出嚟，話完成交易，禁入去可以睇到詳情同Input Data<br />\n冇嘅話手動去Etherscan (Ropsten版) search返自己address <a href=\"https://ropsten.etherscan.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fropsten.etherscan.io%2F&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHl%2BAd7ywbQ%2FyO%2FBW%2BNKOVGM%3D&h=e61fcaea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ropsten.etherscan.io/</a><br />\n7. 禁Click to see more- Input Data- View input as UTF-8<br />\n睇到原本嘅message<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bRsBjQN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbRsBjQN.png&h=6e4d9701&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n例子:  我已經幫七警案wiki資料、聰仔幅相、同埋香港警察條Facebook片做咗Backup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://ropsten.etherscan.io/tx/0x84fc244c0d62d02d6b204d8d7b655b61eca7e5018f639e2cd91317c9ebed7aaa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fropsten.etherscan.io%2Ftx%2F0x84fc244c0d62d02d6b204d8d7b655b61eca7e5018f639e2cd91317c9ebed7aaa&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHl%2BAd7ywbQ%2FyO%2FBW%2BNKOVGM%3D&h=471a8bb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ropsten.etherscan.io/tx/0x84fc244c0d62d02d6b204d8d7b655b61eca7e5018f639e2cd91317c9ebed7aaa</a><br />\n<br />\n風險 &amp; 局限<br />\n1. 理論上address係匿名，唔講冇人知呢個address屬於邊個，除非之後連咗去知道你身份嘅地方，例如交易所<br />\n2. Ethereum測試網絡比主網容易受攻擊癱瘓，但寫過嘅資料未試過被更改<br />\n3. 最適合backup純文字，如想upload圖/片可以去啲唔駛註冊嘅網，但有機會被delete<br />\n片: <a href=\"http://streamable.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHl%2BAd7ywbQ%2FyO%2FBW%2BNKOVGM%3D&h=483dd65e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">streamable.com</a> or dtube<br />\n圖: <a href=\"http://mgbb.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmgbb.com&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHl%2BAd7ywbQ%2FyO%2FBW%2BNKOVGM%3D&h=3ac5838f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">mgbb.com</a><br />\n4. 連出公海仍然要小心IP問題，必要時用VPN, TOR<br />\n<br />\n大家快啲學吓，將啲重要嘢upload上blockchain，以後唔好直接放連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺blockchain忽然發現隱藏訊息其實好平常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n科技救港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀: <br />\n[撐警]仆街 有黃屍惡意將警察個人資料寫左落Ethereum條blockchain到！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1279182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1279182</a><br />\nAnonymous 匿名者要向香港警察宣戰啦！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1279816\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1279816</a>"},{"pid":"11b1572b595b20c5ea850e8a579ece59a3aefb9e","tid":1282435,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:44:03.000Z","msg":"push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" c